main event: On 30 October 1967, an observer reported sighting 3 dish-shaped objects in Garwood, New Jersey, that appeared bright green and glowed while flying at high speeds.
interesting points: The observer initially described the sighting as lasting 30 seconds, but later believed it lasted 9 or 10 minutes,The objects were described as dish-shaped and moving at speeds near 1000 mph,Conflicting points were noted in the report but the observer felt it was an aircraft,Weather conditions were clear at the time of sighting,No physical evidence was found from the observation.
witness description: A 19-year-old female student working as a line clerk
